::Reptilica/DevilDuer/Zardus::

Reptilica lands at the Alliance base, DevilDuer running up seconds later. The 
smaller bot transforms, breathing heavily.

"Couldn't fly any faster?" DevilDuer asks sarcastically in between breaths.

"Sorry, Devil," Reptilica says, chuckling, I thought you could keep up.

"Shut up," DevilDuer says, walking into the base, Reptilica following.

"Zardus," he says into his comm-link, "We have a new bot here. She's ready to 
be reprogrammed."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zardus looks at Soundwave after he recieves Reptilica's message.

"As much as I have enjoyed listening to talks about peace," he says calmly, 
standing up, "I'm afraid it is not in my best interests. I'm sure you 
understand."

He presses a button on his wrist comp, a blast door dropping over the exit as 
autoguns emerge from the corners of the room, one emerging from the middle of 
the cealing, all of them instantly opening fire on Soundwave.

Zardus leans back calmly against a wall, activating his comm-link. "I'll be 
there shortly," he says, sending the transmission to Reptilica.
